Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:56.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shiny Shiny 月光載滿了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:24:04.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}世界是這般精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:06.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不是嗎?
